 ERGen
=======

TPC-E benchmark simulator, using RabbitMQ.


 requirement
-------------
 erlang, R15B03-1
 rabbitmq, 2.8.7
 amqp_client, 2.8.7

 odbc
   mysql, 5.5.x

 building and running
----------------------
 $ unzip -d deps /path/amqp_client-2.8.7-src/dist/amqp_client-2.8.7.ez 
 $ unzip -d deps /path/amqp_client-2.8.7-src/dist/rabbit_common-2.8.7.ez
 $ make build
 $ make run

 Eshell V5.9.3.1  (abort with ^G)
 1> ergen:run().

 or

 1> ergen:run(300). % 300 = interval, ms

 2> ergen:cancel().
